[
  {
    "startTime": 7.8,
    "endTime": 9.19,
    "text": "It all looks so beautiful."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 10.3,
    "endTime": 12.0,
    "text": "The turkey, the stuffing."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 12.0,
    "endTime": 13.91,
    "text": "The cranberries."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 14.281,
    "endTime": 15.0,
    "text": "Enough!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 15.0,
    "endTime": 16.947,
    "text": "A monkey could have made them!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 22.8,
    "endTime": 26.3,
    "text": "Hey, listen guys, we feel really terrible."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 26.3,
    "endTime": 28.365000000000002,
    "text": "He's doing that weird eye-contact thing."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 29.2,
    "endTime": 31.8,
    "text": "Don't look at him. Don't look at him."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 31.8,
    "endTime": 32.7,
    "text": "Come on, you guys."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 32.7,
    "endTime": 37.7,
    "text": "We want you to know we're very, very sorry."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 37.7,
    "endTime": 40.230000000000004,
    "text": "Right guys?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 40.23,
    "endTime": 42.351,
    "text": "- I feel terrible. - Oh, so sorry."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 42.5,
    "endTime": 45.07,
    "text": "Sorry."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 45.07,
    "endTime": 47.6,
    "text": "But let's not ruin this day. You worked so hard."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 47.6,
    "endTime": 50.9,
    "text": "Let's move past this and try to have a nice meal all together."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 50.9,
    "endTime": 55.4,
    "text": "The floating heads do make a good point."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 55.4,
    "endTime": 57.14,
    "text": "Yeah, they do seem to feel pretty bad."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 57.14,
    "endTime": 57.6,
    "text": "So bad."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 57.6,
    "endTime": 58.2,
    "text": "So bad."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 58.2,
    "endTime": 60.639,
    "text": "So bad."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 62.9,
    "endTime": 63.699999999999996,
    "text": "Okay."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 63.7,
    "endTime": 68.4,
    "text": "Okay, you two go get the dessert and I'll let you in."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 68.4,
    "endTime": 70.69300000000001,
    "text": "Dessert?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 71.16,
    "endTime": 71.5,
    "text": "Yeah."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 71.5,
    "endTime": 74.02,
    "text": "I asked you and Phoebe to pick up the pies."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 74.02,
    "endTime": 75.47699999999999,
    "text": "You did remember, right?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 75.477,
    "endTime": 76.7,
    "text": "Pies, oh."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 76.7,
    "endTime": 81.10000000000001,
    "text": "We thought you said prize."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 81.1,
    "endTime": 82.076,
    "text": "Here."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 85.669,
    "endTime": 88.03699999999999,
    "text": "Grand Supreme little darling."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 88.037,
    "endTime": 89.9,
    "text": "Congratulations!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 92.0,
    "endTime": 94.4,
    "text": "Oh my God. You forgot the pies?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 94.4,
    "endTime": 96.0,
    "text": "Well, I can't believe this."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 96.0,
    "endTime": 97.206,
    "text": "You forced me to make dinner."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 97.206,
    "endTime": 102.0,
    "text": "Then you're an hour late and you forget the one little thing that I asked you to do."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 102.0,
    "endTime": 104.549,
    "text": "Really girls, not cool."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 106.0,
    "endTime": 108.47,
    "text": "Well, you man heads aren't any better."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 108.47,
    "endTime": 112.42,
    "text": "You lied about going to the game. You knew it would make you late and you still went anyway."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 112.42,
    "endTime": 114.17,
    "text": "Hey, I'm getting a little tired of this, okay."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 114.17,
    "endTime": 115.149,
    "text": "We said, we're sorry."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 115.149,
    "endTime": 117.0,
    "text": "It's Thanksgiving for Pete's sakes."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 117.4,
    "endTime": 118.44800000000001,
    "text": "A day of forgiveness."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 119.0,
    "endTime": 120.43,
    "text": "It's a day to be thankful."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 120.43,
    "endTime": 123.30000000000001,
    "text": "Don't make me come up there."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 123.3,
    "endTime": 125.0,
    "text": "It's too late for apologies."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 125.0,
    "endTime": 128.0,
    "text": "Fine. Let's just go. I don't need your stupid dinner."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 128.0,
    "endTime": 131.5,
    "text": "That would be a lot more convincing if you weren't drooling."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 131.5,
    "endTime": 133.598,
    "text": "Ew! Is that what that is?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 133.448,
    "endTime": 136.053,
    "text": "Sorry."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 136.053,
    "endTime": 137.16,
    "text": "Come on, you guys."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 137.16,
    "endTime": 139.0,
    "text": "Let's just do our own Thanksgiving."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 139.0,
    "endTime": 140.0,
    "text": "Yeah, I'll cook."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 140.0,
    "endTime": 141.363,
    "text": "Yeah, let's go out."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 141.363,
    "endTime": 144.3,
    "text": "Hey!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 144.3,
    "endTime": 146.29100000000003,
    "text": "Yeah, you three, have a nice Thanksgiving."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 146.291,
    "endTime": 148.75,
    "text": "The three of us?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 148.75,
    "endTime": 148.3,
    "text": "Yeah."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 148.3,
    "endTime": 150.09900000000002,
    "text": "You, Chan and the vein!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 161.0,
    "endTime": 162.0,
    "text": "Uh oh."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 162.0,
    "endTime": 163.02,
    "text": "I'm stuck."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 163.02,
    "endTime": 164.4,
    "text": "Joey, that is not going to work."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 164.4,
    "endTime": 166.292,
    "text": "No, seriously."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 166.1,
    "endTime": 168.04,
    "text": "I'm really wedged in here."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 168.04,
    "endTime": 170.195,
    "text": "I'll pull you through."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 170.195,
    "endTime": 171.47199999999998,
    "text": "Ow, ow, ow! Stop, stop!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 171.472,
    "endTime": 173.48000000000002,
    "text": "I'm worried about damaging my head!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 173.48,
    "endTime": 177.0,
    "text": "It's a little late for that."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 177.0,
    "endTime": 179.0,
    "text": "Hurry up. You got to do something."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 179.0,
    "endTime": 181.0,
    "text": "All right, well, this does not change anything!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 181.2,
    "endTime": 184.0,
    "text": "Okay, we need to get something to grease the sides of his face."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 184.0,
    "endTime": 184.8,
    "text": "Uh, we got turkey grease."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 184.8,
    "endTime": 186.0,
    "text": "Bring it."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 186.0,
    "endTime": 190.8,
    "text": "I just want to say that I'm sorry I referred to the vein as a separate person."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 190.8,
    "endTime": 193.8,
    "text": "Here you go."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 193.8,
    "endTime": 195.5,
    "text": "Oh, that smells good."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 204.0,
    "endTime": 204.8,
    "text": "Okay."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 204.0,
    "endTime": 207.472,
    "text": "Okay, try it."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 208.0,
    "endTime": 209.342,
    "text": "It isn't working!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 210.0,
    "endTime": 212.0,
    "text": "All right, we're going to have to unscrew the chain."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 212.0,
    "endTime": 214.0,
    "text": "Well, hurry! I can't feel my ears."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 214.0,
    "endTime": 215.377,
    "text": "Can you ever feel your ears?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 216.21,
    "endTime": 217.043,
    "text": "Interesting."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 219.587,
    "endTime": 220.40599999999998,
    "text": "Chandler, where are your tools?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 220.406,
    "endTime": 223.555,
    "text": "Oh, I left them on my bulldozer."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 226.3,
    "endTime": 229.0,
    "text": "I don't have tools."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 229.0,
    "endTime": 231.73,
    "text": "Well, I do, but Rachel borrowed them."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 231.0,
    "endTime": 232.202,
    "text": "I lent them to Ross."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 232.202,
    "endTime": 233.362,
    "text": "I gave them to Joey."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 233.362,
    "endTime": 235.384,
    "text": "I left them at the park."
  }
]